      <div class="fl w-80 dib">
        <div>
          <div class="bb b--white-20 pv3">Kechara Forest Retreat <span class="fr light-green">RM80,500</span></div>
          <p class="f6 lh-copy">
            Kechara Forest Retreat was conceptualized by H.E. Tsem Tulku Rinpoche as the heart of the Kechara organization. Located 45 minutes away from the capital city of Malaysia, the beautiful holistic center serves as a sanctuary away from the hustle and bustle for anyone in need of a break from their hectic city lives to rest, relax and recharge. You can read more about the breadth and depth of work that Kechara does here.
          </p>
