      <div class="fl w-20 f3 serif bg-navy pv2">19/06</div>
      <div class="fl w-80 dib">
        <div>
          <div class="bb b--white-20 pv3">Kechara House <span class="fr light-green">RM30,000</span></div>
          <p class="f6 lh-copy">
            Kechara House is a Tibetan Buddhist center founded in 2000 by H. E. Tsem Tulku Rinpoche of Gaden Shartse Monastery. The aim of the centre is to share the ancient, universal wisdom of Buddha’s teachings with practitioners in Malaysia and the surrounding regions. The donation went towards prayers that were done for the spiritual advisor, H.E. Tsem Rinpoche.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
