          <div class="bb b--white-20 pv3">Starship Foundation <span class="fr light-green">RM35,000</span></div>
          <p class="f6 lh-copy">
            Starship Foundation’s vision is to educate, elevate, and empower marginalised communities in East Malaysia (Sabah and Sarawak) through efforts in two fields: education and agriculture. We came to know about Starship Foundation through Terence (an ex-employee of Khailee). Currently serving as the head of the education initiatives, both Terence and his wife, Deborah are fully dedicated towards ensuring that children living below the poverty line are fully supported in their academic life. The couple focuses their efforts on the construction and refurbishment of hostels, which houses children from ages 6-18. Our donation went towards the purchasing of a mobile to transport the children between the hostel and school. You can read more about their story here.
          </p>
